.TH LOOTSHEET-DB-STATUS 1 "Mar 2026" "LootSheet" "LootSheet Manual"
.SH NAME
lootsheet-db-status \\- Show configured database lifecycle state
.SH SYNOPSIS
lootsheet db status [flags]
.SH DESCRIPTION
LootSheet CLI

Usage:
  lootsheet db status

Displays:
  Database path
  Existence and lifecycle state
  Detail for foreign or damaged databases
  Current and target schema versions
  Applied and pending migrations
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
-h, --help
help for status
.SH SEE ALSO
lootsheet-db(1)
